<h3>Culture of Secrecy:-</h3>
<p>Electoral Bond:-</p>
<p>Sealed Envelope:- SC asked for Details of Political funding in sealed envelope .</p>
<p>National Statistical office:- Credibility crisis of GDP Figures, employment Data.</p>
<p>NCRB does not record data on lynchings and religious killings.</p>
<p>This craze for secrecy has affected the RTI process.&nbsp;</p>
